<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285304>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. a – b. Head of female in frontal view. a. S. pulchra sp. nov.; b. S. ferox. c – f. Microsculpture on metapostnotum. c. S. takeuchii sp. nov., d. S. hirasana; e. pulchra sp. nov.; f. S. ferox. g – h. Head of male in lateral view. g. S. sturmii; h. S. jucunda." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/285304/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285300>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Siobla species, lancet. a. S. apicalis, N 20110213 A, Masutomi; b. S. ferox, N 20110109 A, Hakone; c. S. hirasana, N 20110109 B, Hikagezawa; d. S. japonica sp. nov., holotype, N 20131105 C; e. S. jucunda, N 20130423 B, Asahidake-onsen; f. S. metallica, N 20131106 N, Todaigawa; g. S. pulchra sp. nov., holotype, N 20131105 A; h. S. sturmii, N 20130423 A, Mt. Kurodake; i. S. takeuchii sp. nov., holotype, N 20130906 B. Scale bar = 100 Μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/285300/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285301>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Siobla species, middle serrulae (same specimens as in Fig. 6). a. S. apicalis; b. S. ferox; c. S. hirasana; d. S. japonica sp. nov.; e. S. jucunda; f. S. metallica; g. S. pulchra sp. nov.; h. S. sturmii; i. S. takeuchii sp. nov. Scale bar = 100 Μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/285301/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285303>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. a – e. Siobla pulchra sp. nov.. a. Head of female in dorsal view; b. Head of male in dorsal view; c. Head of male in lateral view; d. Ovipositor sheath in lateral view; e. Antenna of female; f – j. S. japonica sp. nov., f. Head of female in dorsal view; g. Head of male in dorsal view; h. Head of female in frontal view; i. Ovipositor sheath in lateral view; j. Antenna of female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/285303/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285305>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. a – d. Siobla takeuchii sp. nov. a. Head of female in dorsal view; b. Head of male in dorsal view; c. Head of female in frontal view; d. Subgenital plate. e – h. S. hirasana. e. Head of female in dorsal view; f. Head of male in dorsal view; g. Head of female in frontal view; h. Subgenital plate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/285305/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285302>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Siobla species, a – i. gonoforceps & j – r. penis valve. a, j. S. apicalis, N 20130430 A, Mt. Hayachine; b, k. S. ferox, N 20131106 G, Amagasa; c, l. S. hirasana, N 20110108 B (c) and N 20130907 C (l), Hikagezawa; d, m. S. japonica sp. nov., paratype, N 20131105 D, Marunuma; e, n. S. jucunda, N 20130423 D, Minoto; f, o. S. metallica, N 20100313 C, Kiyosato; g, p. S. pulchra sp. nov., paratype, N 20131105 B, Nakayama-toge; h, q. S. sturmii, N 20130423 C, Asahidake-onsen; i, r. S. takeuchii sp. nov., paratype, N 20130901 F, Mt. Kenashi-yama. Scale bar = 100 Μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/285302/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

